 longer: 1 inch or 1 centimeter?","a":"1 inch","h":"1 inch is about 2.5 centimeters. Inches are bigger!","e":"📐"}],"qBank":[{"t":"A pencil ends at 7 on a ruler. How long is the pencil?<svg width=\"354\" height=\"104\" viewBox=\"0 0 177 52\" style=\"display:block;margin:6px auto;border-radius:6px;background:#f9f9f9\"><rect x=\"10\" y=\"8\" width=\"119\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#2980b9\" rx=\"3\" opacity=\"0.85\"/><text x=\"70\" y=\"15\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"white\" font-weight=\"bold\">pencil</text><line x1=\"129\" y1=\"8\" x2=\"129\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"0.7\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,2\" opacity=\"0.6\"/><rect x=\"10\" y=\"22\" width=\"153\" height=\"12\" fill=\"#fff8e7\" stroke=\"#c8a000\" stroke-width=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/><line x1=\"18\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"18\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"35\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"35\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"52\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"52\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"69\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"69\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"86\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"86\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"103\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"103\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"120\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"120\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"137\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"137\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"154\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"154\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><text x=\"10\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#444\">0\"</text><line x1=\"27\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"27\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><text x=\"27\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#444\">1\"</text><line x1=\"44\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"44\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><text x=\"44\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\