 you use to measure a pencil?","o":["Centimeters","Feet","Millimeters","Inches"],"a":3,"e":"Inches are used for small objects like a pencil.","d":"e"},{"t":"Where should you start measuring on a ruler?<svg width=\"288\" height=\"104\" viewBox=\"0 0 144 52\" style=\"display:block;margin:6px auto;border-radius:6px;background:#f9f9f9\"><rect x=\"10\" y=\"22\" width=\"120\" height=\"12\" fill=\"#fff8e7\" stroke=\"#c8a000\" stroke-width=\"0.8\" rx=\"1\"/><line x1=\"20\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"40\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"40\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"60\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"60\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"100\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"100\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"120\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"120\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#aaa\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><text x=\"10\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#444\">0\"</text><line x1=\"30\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"30\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><text x=\"30\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#444\">1\"</text><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><text x=\"50\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#444\">2\"</text><line x1=\"70\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"70\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><text x=\"70\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#444\">3\"</text><line x1=\"90\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"90\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><text x=\"90\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#444\">4\"</text><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"34\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><text x=\"110\" y=\"40\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"5\" fill=\"#444\">5\"</text><line x1=